<Section title="com.io7m.montarre.flatpak"
         xmlns="urn:com.io7m.structural:8:0"
         id="ded1ac99-9556-4ef9-b01f-3f689a164733">
  <Subsection title="Overview">
    <Paragraph>
      The <Term type="module">com.io7m.montarre.flatpak</Term> packager creates
      <LinkExternal target="https://www.flatpak.org">Flatpaks</LinkExternal>.
    </Paragraph>
  </Subsection>

  <Subsection title="Outputs">
    <Paragraph>
      Given a <Link target="9d02d402-92ae-4267-be43-1ebb08e8e1bc">package name</Link>, the output of the packager will
      be <Term type="file">${PACKAGE_NAME}.flatpak</Term>
      unconditionally.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      An example output of the packager is <Term type="file">com.io7m.montarre.flatpak</Term>.
    </Paragraph>
  </Subsection>
</Section>
